{"tid":1634074,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（低能粗製慎入） 白布澄清抺黑","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:22.000Z","uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f246e7022f1447117ebd6bebee0659eec9b08e05","tid":1634074,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"其實有好多藍屍係畀CcTVB洗腦 <br />\n又有好多外國人想了解香港喱場運動 <br />\n但又冇方法 <br />\n如果大家有能力做外國文宣就幫幫手 <br />\n翻譯 PS 也好<br />\n<br />\n作為英文中文都係得level three 嘅電腦和理非<br />\n我淨係諗到出賣自己肉體 做人肉連儂<br />\n但平時memo紙太細張 好難睇 <br />\n於是就用左喱幾個月嚟都冇着過嘅白色衫 <br />\n用嚟做我的連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n白T or白布 <br />\nmarker <br />\n萬字夾or扣針<br />\n<br />\n第一步 拎白布同肥美大脾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/988VLfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F988VLfJ.jpg&h=9cc8a7d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二步 盡訴心中情<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpX0bWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpX0bWr.jpg&h=13e67569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三步 剪出嚟 貼係身上 書包上 袋上<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NkP9PKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkP9PKm.jpg&h=f7c7f239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：對唔住我太肥 件衫太大遮鳩住成個背囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚廢 打完篇嘢自己睇都笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63549e837b8f11df566ab18abc826f44a8f0481","tid":1634074,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"善心打破0 回覆"}]}